'''Dipika O'Neill Joti''' is an actress who portrayed [[Depa Billaba]] in [[Star Wars: Episode I The Phantom Menace|''Star Wars'': Episode I ''The Phantom Menace'']]. Footage of Billaba and other [[Jedi High Council]] members from that film was reused for [[Star Wars: Episode II Attack of the Clones|''Star Wars'': Episode II ''Attack of the Clones'']], although Joti filmed no new footage for the second installment.<ref name="Star Wars: The Lightsaber Collection" />

